Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's coming here and isn't hanging out with us lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lately, she's been going to this park everyday to meet some guy named Bruce or Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, she might have a foreign boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what we came to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you too curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not too curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We want to know if this person is suitable for Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, you're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This could play a big role in Ayumi's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, is it that serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Ta" character in the word "Tanbo".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,Tanbo = paddy field, "Ta" character = ç”°
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, with only four matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta character, Ta character...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't I break the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I give up, how do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:02:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really did make the Ta character!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was also taken from this quiz book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are, your foot has really healed, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Steve, your skin disease is almost gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, give this medicine to Steve please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Steve?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Steve don't move, be still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jackie and Steve were just cats' names.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, and we were almost worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it would end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bruce, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Baa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're handing that cat over to me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you suddenly yelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cat got under my car's hood again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it also peed in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for taking care of that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These wild cats should be abandoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides wherever you parked your car, isn't it off-limits?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't complain just because a cat took a pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take the cat's place and be taught a lesson!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you kids!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't forgive someone bullying weaker people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Baa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that cat goes under my hood again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Bruce,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you, don't go under hoods?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're such a prankster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You boys saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, you guys were so brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not helping these stray cats, isn't something I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know right, besides Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s like a god to these cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm nowhere near a god, nor that kind of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a cowardly person who can't protect them by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of these cats were abandoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People did that on their own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While looking for someone who will adopt these cats, Shizuka-obaachan is taking care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to help her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could've told us, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, you're part of the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we've solved many complicated cases up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, cases huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is there something that's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, can you hold on to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well I need to go somewhere in the morning; lately my Neuralgia's been acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neuralgia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you should go to the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot springs huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lately, I've been going to the Izu springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an inn I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, I'm putting you in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no sign of Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably basking in the sun somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuka-obaachan is taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's always here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably went to the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, she did mention that her Neuralgia's been acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} wouldn't leave the cats alone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did she suddenly become ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we go to Â©baa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, she said something that bothered me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, it's me Ayumi, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, it's me Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something may have happened to her after we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're thinking too much Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:30.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that guy from yesterday said he'd teach Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange, the evening paper from yesterday is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, she didn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't come home!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, she couldn't have gone directly to the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then something must've happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you call the fire department, Mitsuhiko you call the police station,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please see if you can find a person named Oomori Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of all of the people who were involved in an accident yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, you find out who that guy from yesterday was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he always parks illegally, someone near the park probably noticed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look in the vicinity and try to find an acquaintance of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, time for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nor that kind of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a cowardly person who can't protect them by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope it's just me imagination things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I have known each other for a long time but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have any friends or relatives that live nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why she wouldn't leave the cats alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lately she's been going through a lot, maybe she went to the hot springs to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going through a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an old man named Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who lived alone near the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} made it her job to take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, exactly a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unexpectedly, Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell over in the bathtub, hit his head really hard, and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looked like he was set up to fall on the faucet, even though it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Shizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} became lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was alive, she would always refer to him as her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always taking him to the Izu hot springs, she took great care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izu hot springs huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where they always stayed in Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know .but if you go to Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house you might be able to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now his nephew is living there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is a president of a company at Haido city, whose name is Mochizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the place Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the hot springs full of memories Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took her to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where she went!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know it because the name Oomori Shizuka was not mentioned in the traffic accidents or in any cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hot spring where Uncle and Shizuka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} frequently went to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, do you know exactly where they stayed in Izu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mochizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We want to be sure we'll start transferring the lockers at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door will never open, so there's some old stuff in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only junk so you can throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izu hot springs huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never heard of that but don't worry, she should be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of ornaments of apes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are all from Uncle's collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are the three wise monkeys right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you seem to know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're Mizaru (don't see), Iwazaru (don't talk), and Kikazaru (don't hear).
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three monkeys are reminders not to do sinful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked about him everywhere, and I still haven't found out who that guy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try calling the Izu hotel and other hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Izu"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But here are lots of places called that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we can't just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really want to know if Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is safe or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look it's, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bruce bad news, Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'^wrong Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bruce had Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s scarf around his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, Bruce was with that old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something written on the scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the kanji "hi" written eight times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:27.19,Signs,,0,0,0,,"Hi" means day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, there's a stain on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bloodstain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s been kidnapped and locked somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't go to the Izu hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, since Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} made Bruce wear this bloody scarf, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's locked somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't she injured and can't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then she would've wrote where she is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she wrote this code, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A code!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, if by any chance the culprit found it, he wouldn't know what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we five to solve this code right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} would call the cats, she'd always give me a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the questions said to add one stroke to the character "hi" to make a different kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Q-Quiz huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko, do you understand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By adding a horizontal stroke inside, it becomes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,"Me" means eye
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By adding a vertical stroke, we get the ta from tanbou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adding a tiny diagonal stroke on top gives us shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,"Shiro" means white
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there Mitsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there anymore, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kyu, yoshi, kou, tan, shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kyu-yoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kou-tan-shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll write it down for you guys right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From left to right:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, shiro, ta, kyu, yoshi, kou, tan, shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot of characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So do these characters represent where Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would the first three words mean "Mejiro's rice field"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any fields in Mejiro, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When it snows, the field will become white.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then... Then... Then eyes starts dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you think of something, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meshirota is living alone at the former Yoshikou place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't change a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyways, we need to figure out the meaning of the remaining five characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first word kyu is taken from shinkyu, meaning old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next word, yoshi is taken from riyu, meaning motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kou meaning shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tan means the sun above the horizon, which has the meaning of morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen this character before on a New Year's card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the tan in gantan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gantan refers to the morning of New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,New Year's card?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the last character, shin, means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:16:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, in the 12 signs of the Chinese zodiac, this character means "monkey".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does it have to do with someone being born in the year of the monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This character tan, couldn't it also be read dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dan taken from danna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, meaning "master of the house." does use this^character...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you mentioned that Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} called Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} her "husband."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, so it's these two characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Combining kyu with tan gives us "former husband."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which adds up to be Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I thought Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} wanted to tell us where she's locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember yesterday when she said that she's a cowardly person?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a cowardly person who can't protect them by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, does that mean that her Neuralgia wasn't acting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} found out a secret about Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which lead to her abduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she wanted to tell us this secret by making this code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, the character "ta" is made by combining the characters "kuchi" and "juu" correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By using the character ta, if you put an "X" to kuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it mean not to tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No that's not it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means to shut his mouth, which means murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look carefully, if you line it up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Explains the reason why he was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death wasn't an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone murdered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also the remaining four characters tell us the reason, and what the murder weapon was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remaining characters are me, shiro, kou, and shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, shiro, kou, and shin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Koushin"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.67,Signs,,0,0,0,,Konshin is a folk faith in Japan with Chinese Taoist origins, influenced by Shintou, Buddhism and other local beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was a code to make Koushin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koushin as in the "Koushin Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, by a train station there's "Koushin Street" that's in a shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, does it mean someone over there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No that's not it, as Mitsuhiko mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Koushin Tower," there's something hidden inside.\N40!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three wise monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the see, speak, and see no evil monkeys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ornaments of the three apes that we saw at Ezaki-sans house,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the weapon used to murder Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the remaining characters, me and shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try remembering^he ornaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so it's one of the apes with white eyes correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Mochizuki is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyways, we're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 2 o'clock, Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} will be carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You figured out where Obaa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's definitely there, there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the help of our report the police arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were able to safely rescue Shizuka-obaachan f rom the locker that was about to get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, coinciding with Shizuka-obaachan's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bloodstains were found on the ornaments of the three wise monkeys
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:11.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mochizuki was arrested for murder, kidnapping, and imprisonment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuka-obaachan is fully recovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's taking care of the cats again.
